<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٤٧ ... سُورَةُ مُحَمَّدٍ ... آياتها ٣٨ مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَضَلَّ أَعْمَالَهُمْ}</span> ... أَحْبَطَهَا، وَأَبْطَلَهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَفَّرَ}</span> ... أَزَالَ، وَمَحَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَالَهُمْ}</span> ... حَالَهُمْ وَشَانَهُمْ فِي الدُّنْيَا وَالآخِرَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبَاطِلَ}</span> ... الشَّيْطَانَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَضَرْبَ الرِّقَابِ}</span> ... اضْرِبُوا مِنْهُمُ الأَعْنَاقَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَثْخَنتُمُوهُمْ}</span> ... أَضْعَفْتُمُوهُمْ بِكَثْرَةِ القِتَالِ، وَكَسَرْتُمْ شَوْكَتَهُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَشُدُّوا الْوَثَاقَ}</span> ... أَحْكِمُوا قَيْدَ الأَسْرَى.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَنًّا}</span> ... تَمُنُّونَ عَلَيْهِمْ بِإِطْلَاقِ الأَسْرَى مِنْ غَيْرِ عِوَضٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِدَاءً}</span> ... تَطْلُبُونَ مِنْهُمْ فِدْيَةً تُخَلِّصُهُمْ مِنَ الأَسْرِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَتَّى تَضَعَ الْحَرْبُ أَوْزَارَهَا}</span> ... أَثْقَالَها؛<span class="c5"> وَالمُرَادُ:</span> حَتَّى تَنْتَهِيَ الحَرْبُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِّيَبْلُوَ}</span> ... لِيَخْتَبِرَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُضِلَّ أَعْمَالَهُمْ}</span> ... يُبْطِلَ ثَوَابَ أَعْمَالِهِمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَالَهُمْ}</span> ... شَانَهُمْ فِي الدُّنْيَا وَالآخِرَةِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَرَّفَهَا لَهُمْ}</span> ... بَيَّنَهَا لَهُمْ؛ فَيَهْتَدُونَ إِلَى مَسَاكِنِهِمْ فِيهَا مِنْ غَيْرِ اسْتِدْلَالٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيُثَبِّتْ أَقْدَامَكُمْ}</span> ... يُثَبِّتْكُمْ عِنْدَ القِتَالِ، وَيُقَوِّ قُلُوبَكُمْ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>